145
00:14:18,054 --> 00:14:21,274
 School's boring. I'm going out to make my own way. 

146
00:14:21,274 --> 00:14:25,594
 Why leave now? Aren't you about to take
the college entrance exams? 

147
00:14:26,174 --> 00:14:31,394
