159
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:14,154
 stop messing around. Study hard and get serious. 

160
00:15:14,154 --> 00:15:15,690
 Be good. 

161
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:19,850
 Alright, I'm leaving. 

162
00:15:51,514 --> 00:15:53,314
What are you doing?

163
00:15:59,854 --> 00:16:04,730
Your mom's drunk.

164
00:16:04,730 --> 00:16:07,090
I'll go now.

165
00:16:07,094 --> 00:16:08,630
Stop.

166
00:16:09,210 --> 00:16:11,710
Do you like my mom?

167
00:16:11,714 --> 00:16:14,914
Don't talk nonsense.
How could I possibly like your mom?

168
00:16:14,914 --> 00:16:20,754
I don't hate you,
but my parents aren't divorced yet.

169
00:16:20,754 --> 00:16:23,494
And I'm not ready for a new dad soon.

170
00:16:23,494 --> 00:16:26,754
Go home and think about it. Don't rush.

171
00:16:26,754 --> 00:16:30,854
I don't want to be your new dad.
What's there to consider? I'm leaving.

172
00:16:30,854 --> 00:16:34,634
Tuck your mom in.
Take her shoes off and look after her.

173
00:16:34,634 --> 00:16:35,834
Wait.

174
00:16:35,834 --> 00:16:37,114
What now?

175
00:16:37,114 --> 00:16:39,574
Turn off the light and lock the door.

176
00:16:39,574 --> 00:16:41,774
Yeah, yeah. So many instructions.

177
00:16:46,654 --> 00:16:48,434
Your light is broken.

178
00:17:01,594 --> 00:17:06,554
That little brat.
How could I possibly like your mom?

179
00:17:07,114 --> 00:17:11,274
Cheng Kai Ran likes Fang Ya En.

180
00:17:13,894 --> 00:17:18,274
